| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-0407 — Recovery Inhibition (lockbit3)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 38ec8eec-a560-5078-9dc7-6b3d83a1dda7"
